99_7621650644553269_1655627145384024300_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7XsKaKpseXUQ7kNvgHC-M9C&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCKdi18uGlZtKgjVsfN1EKrqV379EKT7jwA9faI2rTQrg&oe=6720C09D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Project_Y: Working Title", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This game is an English/Japanese version.\nEnglish text and Japanese are supported.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR.\n\n\n- It comes with \"\"noise\"\" -\n\nOnce you have watched the video, you must find all the ``sinister beings'' recorded in the video.\nThat's the only way to escape.\n\nAnd when I found out everything,\n\u201cSomething\u201d happens\u2026\"", "short_description": "This game is an English/Japanese version.\nEnglish text and Japanese are supported.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "ca_4_1080x360.png", "id": "25313306218313815", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982665_25313306228313814_5685240816022121286_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sZBuhAS5ZV8Q7kNvgHuViLl&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculus